# LogWeaverMap

LogWeaverMap transforms raw, distributed log streams into an interactive spatial interface for better anomaly detection and trend analysis.

## Features
- Interactive node-based map for log origins.
- Real-time log ingestion via WebSocket or Kafka.
- Pattern-based log highlighting with anomaly flags.
- Support for custom metrics overlays.

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-org/LogWeaverMap.git
